      <head>Gustav Wustmann</head>

      <div>
        <p>German philologist and historian.</p>

        <p>Author of books on Leipzig, its history, architecture, and painting, his most famous work
          is <title level="m">Allerhand Sprachdummheiten: Kleine deutsche Grammatik des
            Zweifelhaften, des Falschen und des H&#xE4;sslichen</title> [A Great Many Language
          Stupidities: Short German Grammar of the Dubious, the False, and the Hideous] (1891,
          4/1908), which aroused much opposition.</p>
      </div>
